      "title": "## Overview",
      "content": "This plan outlines a custom-built Smart Inventory & Sales Management System with AI Demand Forecasting. Due to the complexity and specific technology stack requested, this system cannot be fully implemented using standard Wix Apps or Wix CMS. The plan focuses on the core functionalities that would be part of such a custom application."
    },
    {
      "id": "key-features",
      "title": "## Key features",
      "content": "- **User Authentication with Roles**: Allows users to log in with different permission levels (admin, staff, manager).\n- **Product and Inventory Management**: Enables management of product details and current stock levels.\n- **Real-time Stock Tracking**: Provides up-to-date information on product availability.\n- **Low-Stock Alerts**: Notifies users when inventory for a product falls below a defined threshold.\n- **Sales Management**: Handles the process of creating orders, generating invoices, and managing payments.\n- **AI-Based Demand Forecasting**: Utilizes AI to predict future product demand.\n- **Analytics Dashboard**: Presents key business metrics and insights.\n- **Reporting**: Generates detailed reports on sales, inventory, and forecasts.\n- **Notifications**: Sends alerts and updates to users based on system events."
    },
    {
      "id": "structure",
      "title": "## Structure",
      "content": "- **Dashboard**: The central hub displaying analytics, notifications, and quick access to management functions.\n- **Inventory Management**: Screens for managing products, stock levels, and alerts.\n- **Sales Management**: Screens for processing orders, invoices, and payments.\n- **AI Forecasting**: Interface for viewing demand forecasts.\n- **Reporting Section**: Area for generating and viewing various business reports.\n- **User Management**: Section for managing users and their roles."
    }
